com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.database.serialize

Interface SerializerInjected

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParameterArraySerializer, ParameterSerializer, StandardTransactionIdSerializer, TypeDefinitionDescriptionSerializer

    public interface SerializerInjected
    Marks a AttributeSerializer that requires a Serializer to serialize the internal state. It is expected that the serializer is passed into this object upon initialization and before usage. Furthermore, such serializers will convert the WriteBuffer passed into the AttributeSerializer's write methods to be cast to DataOutput.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
